#

Traditional Beef Borscht

110 min
$15
250 kcal
Difficulty: 40%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Fat

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodSoupBeetBeef

Description

A hearty and comforting beet soup with tender beef, perfect for warming up on a chilly day.

Ingredients

  • beef chuck roast: 1 pound
  • beets: 2 large, peeled and grated
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrots: 2, diced
  • potatoes: 2, diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • fresh dill: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • sour cream: for serving
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • bay leaves: 2
